  [Text] A footnote on this day of national mourning: 
President Salinas de Gortari received [Canadian] Prime Minister 
Chretien. 
  The day is very hot, and at a closed-door meeting Chretien 
and Salinas talked about matters related to NAFTA. They 
highlighted the benefits it represents for Mexico and Canada. 
