<H3> <TI>   January Oil Production Statistics Reported </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  PY2503015994 FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>
<F P=103> PY2503015994 </F>
<F P=104>  FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>



<TEXT>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Editorial Report] Buenos Aires LA NACION in Spanish on 8 
March publishes on page 9 a 300-word unattributed article on oil 
production. The article says Government Oil Deposits "increased 
oil production 24 percent" in January compared with the same 
month last year. It adds that oil exports totalled 525,004 cubic 
meters compared with the 73,227 cubic meters exported in January 
1993. 

</TEXT>

