<F P=102>  FL2803222494 Havana Radio Reloj Network in Spanish 2021 GMT 
28 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> FL2803222494 </F>
<F P=104>  Havana Radio Reloj Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Spanish </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Politburo member Alfredo Hondal Gonzalez, first 
secretary of the Communist Party of Cuba [PCC] in Ciego de Avila 
Province, called for efficiency in the sugar industry during a 
plenum of that organization in Ciego de Avila. Hondal added that 
there are real possibilities of being able to meet the assigned 
sugar plan; to accomplish this, the industry must grind 
efficiently, now that the harvest is in its most productive 
period. The plenum also reviewed the results obtained in 1993 
regarding defense, production by local industries, recreation, 
and tourism. 
  With regard to defense, the party plenum highlighted the 
need to increase political work, with the help of party cadres, 
and to boost the work of declaring zones defense-ready in the 
second stage. 

