<F P=102>  FL2803214394 Port-au-Prince Radio Metropole in French 1700 
GMT 28 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> FL2803214394 </F>
<F P=104>  Port-au-Prince Radio Metropole </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> French </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] On 25 March, the president of the Chamber of 
Deputies called a meeting of a delegation of Haitian legislators 
and political leaders at the KINAM Hotel. Their discussion 
revolved around the crisis resolution plan approved on 2 March 
by the Chamber of Deputies. In this framework, the participants 
reiterated their conviction that that plan takes into account 
the main parties involved in the conflict. 
  The participants also discussed the crisis in the Senate of 
the Republic. They unanimously agreed to send a public, 
patriotic, and urgent call to the Senate and its president to 
meet immediately in order to examine and pass the resolution 
text approved by the Chamber of Deputies. 

