Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [From the "This Very Day" newscast] </F>
  [Text] According to President Reina's private secretary 
[not further identified], Discua Elvir's opinion on voluntary 
and educational military service does not represent the military 
institution's position. This is how the president's office has 
reacted to General Discua's saying he did not know why this type 
